  "title": "Kitchen Crew for Self-Service Concept - FT or PT",
  "description": "<p><em>Casual self-service concept serving up yakitori/skewer dons.</em></p><p><strong>Working Hours & Info:</strong></p><p>•⁠ ⁠Location: Near Kent Ridge MRT at NUS Campus</p><p>•⁠ Fulltime Working Hours: ⁠6 Days</p><p>•⁠ ⁠PT Work: Min 68 hrs/mth ($11 - $13/hr) Depending on experience/skill.<br />•⁠ ⁠Please indicate full-time or otherwise.</p><p><strong>(A) KITCHEN CREW</strong></p><p><em>Responsibilities:</em></p><p>• ⁠Assist in food preparation & cooking tasks.</p><p>• Assist in monitoring and managing kitchen inventory, including restocking.</p><p>• Ensure the quality of food and adherence to SOPs.</p><p>• Work together to ensure smooth operations and timely food prep. Assist in cleaning duties.</p><p>• Comply with food safety & hygiene requirements.</p><p>• Work with kitchen to clean down equipment and station etc.</p><p>• Flexibility to handle various tasks & adapt to changing priorities in kitchen.</p><p>•⁠ ⁠Assist as assigned by the mgmt.</p><p><u><em>Requirements:</em></u></p><p>•⁠ ⁠We welcome applications from individuals of all backgrounds.</p><p>•⁠ ⁠We are only able to hire: Singaporeans / PR / LTVP w/ Letter of Consent at present.</p><p>•⁠ ⁠Part Time Roles also available.</p><p><strong>Join Us!</strong></p><p>Please WA Clare at https://wa.me/6589632326</p>",
